Nigerian artiste Ruger was forced to cut short his performance at an event after a female fan sexually assaulted him. A woman at the front row grabbed his genitals as he entertained the crowd at the Industry Night event in Nigeria. An angry Ruger stormed off the stage a few moments after the incident. Many fans condemned the whole scenario. cassiebrendah64 said that was wrong and disrespectful. "Such acts can be a trigger, especially for someone who has been a victim of sexual abuse." Nairobi.diaries: "If it was a woman performing and a guy touched her like that, it would have been a different kind of conversation and that video would have gone viral. Protect the men, too." ladygwenmedia advised the organisers to send an apology to Ruger for being assaulted at their event.